.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
There 7 different types of food: cranberry, cucumber, eggplant, nectarine, peach, raspberry, watermelon
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, aristoff, cain, swisher, ritmeester, bongani, oliveros
 1. the ritmeester-smoker is the person eating nectarine##1
 2. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
 3. the bongani-smoker is on the far right##1
 4. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
 5. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
 6. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
 7. the ritmeester-smoker is in the middle##1
 8. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the person eating peach##1
 9. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
10. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Food          | cranberry | cucumber | peach | nectarine | raspberry | watermelon | eggplant |
| Cigar   | aristoff      | cain   | swisher   | ritmeester      | fonseca       | oliveros       | bongani     |

