.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-6::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, coffee, iced-tea, juice, soy-milk, sprite
The people have 7 different hobbies: board-games, video-games, woodworking, card-games, cooking, sudoku, photography
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 2. the person drinking 7up is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 3. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 4. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 5. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is in the middle##1
 8. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
10. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4     |    5    |   6   |      7      |
| Beverage    | coffee | soy-milk   | 7up | iced-tea | sprite  | juice | almond-milk |
| Hobby   | card-games   | cooking | board-games | sudoku     | video-games | photography | woodworking   |

