.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-7::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: coral, black, ebony, red, emerald, blue, ivory
The people use 7 different means of transport: boat, jet-ski, motorbike, roller, skateboard, snowmobile, trike
 1. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 2. the person who likes red is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
 3. the person who likes ivory is the person driving the roller##1
 4. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person who likes black##1
 5. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 6. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 7. the person driving the boat is the person who likes ebony##1
 8. the person who likes emerald is in the middle##1
 9. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1
10. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person who likes black##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Color   | coral  | ivory | red | emerald | blue     | black | ebony |
| Transport     | snowmobile | roller      | trike | motorbike    | skateboard | jet-ski   | boat  |

